MXVX extends viewing experience

Goal

MXVX's goal is as its name implies: to extend the viewing experience on tvOS

Product requirement (ongoing)

- Provide the widest codec compatibilities using libVLC and/or libMPV

- Incorporates better content discovery of local media and available online streaming services

- Provide Featurette when available

- Thumbnails when seeking

- Subtitle compatibilities

- Provide technical details of local resources




